                {
                    "id": "snd_info_2",
                    "text": "Here, i use sine waves in some sort off additive synthesis. I use very small steps for pitches  in [EDO]{https://en.xen.wiki/w/EDO} (EDO 2048). Sometimes chords, sometimes arpeggios, then i feed a reverb made with [Max/Msp]{https://cycling74.com/products/max} (yafr2) with the sine waves.||The **picture** is the actual end positions for the game which genrated the sound you're listening to.",
                    "visible": 1,
                    "config": {
                        "image_url": "/images/GO_XD/go_game_00.png",
                        "text_position": "left",
                        "font_size": "15px",
                        "image_visible": "1",
                        "image_position": "right",
                        "image_width": "280px",
                        "image_height": "180px",
                        "image_fit": "contain",
