                        "image_crop": "center",
                        "background_color": "default",
                        "foreground_color": "default"
                    }
                },
                {
                    "id": "snd_info_3",
                    "text": "**more info :** this is a 13 x 13 [goban]{https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Go_equipment#Goban}. I use the lines and columns as binary numbers (13 bits here), using either the black or the white stones as 1 and the empty intersections as 0, sometimes big endian, sometimes small endian.",
